KIS5t_F5hx-0zaMbGVvczhnqNGGHa0D-e64PuQ2FcMGJuSP0I9QZmFBfUCEXl47FBkVQIOWhOmr=
JPbSv-i_4BICaFBg]: =E2=80=9Ca reliable clock makes network synchronization =
very simple. When synchronization is simple the resulting network can be bl=
azing fast, bound only by network bandwidth.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
Just five months into his time at Dropbox, Anatoly quit to build his blockc=
hain. By November 2017, he=E2=80=99d written and published the Solana White=
