FSlX2qW_Ff9A9XAIRY" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">A=
natoly Yakovenko</a> told me is &#8220;the implementation of the arrow of t=
ime in math.&#8221; Sounds mind-bending, and it is, but what it means is th=
at <strong>transactions on Solana are verifiably ordered without all nodes =
needing to agree simultaneously.</strong> That&#8217;s what makes it so fas=
t.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 1em 0;">It also means that Solana can be <strong>single-shard<=
/strong>. While Eth2 is expected to reach 100k TPS, it, and other new block=
