ie back into the main Ethereum blockchain. Solana does everything on one si=
ngle chain, in a single state.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-si=
ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Solana might have the best=
 tech of any blockchain on the market, but the best tech is wasted without =
a strong community of developers and users. The Solana community is strong =
and passionate. You can spot them by the Pit Viper shades in their pfps and=
 &#9678;&#8217;s where o&#8217;s should be. But it needed something to take=
 it crypto mainstream.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line=
-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Which brings us back to those Degenerate=
